Description.LocalizedString: A stronghold that reappears every century.
An ancient structure of clockwork machinery and hidden paths.
A dusty table covered with obscure books.
A relic from a film that would never be.
Recovered from the ruins of a 15th-century castle.
A romantic keepsake from centuries past.
One of the three glyphs of Dominus.
A glowing candle amidst the night.
The sign of a doomed production.
A creature forged to purge the world.
